@startuml architecture
node "Client Device" {
    component "Web Browser" {
        [Frontend App]
        [Mic API]
    }
}

node "Cloud Server" {
    node "Application Server" {
        component "Express.js Backend" as BE
        component "Auth Module"
        component "Recording Manager"
    }

    node "ML Microservice" {
        component "Python Flask API" as ML
        component "Librosa DSP"
        component "Scikit-Learn Model"
    }
    
    database "MongoDB Cluster" {
        [User Data]
        [GridFS Storage]
    }
}

[Frontend App] <--> BE : REST API / WebSocket
BE <--> [User Data] : Mongoose
BE <--> [GridFS Storage] : Streams
BE <--> ML : HTTP (Internal Network)
ML --> [Librosa DSP]
[Librosa DSP] --> [Scikit-Learn Model]
@enduml
